00:19:22,070 --> 00:19:25,610
一年前他让开曼群岛上 好几家赌场洗底
A year ago he cleaned out a couple of casinos in the Cayman Islands.

327
00:19:26,160 --> 00:19:28,370
他从赌场赢了我们两百万…
Downstairs he takes us for $2 million...

328
00:19:28,540 --> 00:19:32,290
又从酒店套房拿了免费的 肥皂、洗发精与毛巾
and upstairs he takes free soap, shampoo and towels.

329
00:19:32,630 --> 00:19:35,910
又是一个 喜爱免费套房…
Another billionaire cheapskate who loved his free rooms...

330
00:19:36,050 --> 00:19:39,170
免费私人飞机又赚得我们两百万 的亿万富翁小气鬼
free private jets and $2 million of our money.

331
00:19:40,840 --> 00:19:42,010
我们也不好惹
But we got him back.

332
00:19:42,140 --> 00:19:44,680
我让机师告诉他飞机故障
I had our pilot tell him the plane was on the fritz.

333
00:19:44,810 --> 00:19:47,130
-发生什么事？ -非常抱歉
ICHlKAWA: What went wrong? BILLY: I'm awfully sorry.

334
00:19:47,980 --> 00:19:49,850
是机械故障
These mechanical things happen.

335
00:19:49,980 --> 00:19:52,270
在这儿总比在上面好
Better here than up there.

336
00:19:52,650 --> 00:19:55,190
然后他赶不上回日本的飞机
SAM: Then he missed the flights connecting with Japan.

337
00:19:55,320 --> 00:19:57,690
竟然没有空房
I can't believe there's no room.

338
00:20:02,580 --> 00:20:05,950
我们给了他一整楼的房间
SAM: We got him back with a whole floor of rooms to himself.

339
00:20:06,080 --> 00:20:07,560
-真抱歉让你赶不上飞机
-Sorry you missed your plane.

340
00:20:07,560 --> 00:20:09,040
-你想要赢回我的钱啊
-You'd like some of my money back.

341
00:20:09,170 --> 00:20:10,960
不，不赌了
Oh, no. No gambling.

342
00:20:13,880 --> 00:20:16,550
他回来后开始下小注
SAM: And once he was back, he played small.

343
00:20:19,510 --> 00:20:22,880
一把只赌一千 而不是平常的三万一把
He bet $1,000 a hand, instead of his usual $30,000 a hand.

344
00:20:26,560 --> 00:20:29,430
但我知道这些豪赌客的习性…
But I knew the trick with whales like Ichikawa...

345
00:20:29,570 --> 00:20:32,020
他们不可能一直下小注的
was that they can't bet small for long.

346
00:20:32,110 --> 00:20:34,480
他不觉得是赢一万…
He didn't think of it as winning $10, 000...

347
00:20:34,570 --> 00:20:37,030
他会想成是输九万…
he thought of it as losing $90, 000.

348
00:20:37,870 --> 00:20:39,740
所以他开始加码
So, he upped his bets.

349
00:20:43,880 --> 00:20:47,920
直到他将赢得的输光 再加上自己一百万的现金
Until he dropped his winnings back and gave up $1 million of his own cash.

350
00:20:50,880 --> 00:20:53,750
在赌场里，第一原则就是 让他们一直赌…
In a casino, the cardinal rule is to keep them playing...

351
00:20:53,890 --> 00:20:55,260
也让他们一直回来
and keep them coming back.

352
00:20:55,390 --> 00:20:57,930
赌得越多就输得越多
The longer they play, the more they lose.

353
00:20:58,060 --> 00:21:00,100
最终钱就都是我们的
In the end, we get it all.

354
00:21:09,570 --> 00:21:12,770
在赌城，每个人都得注意着别人
In Vegas, everybody's gotta watch everybody else.

355
00:21:15,870 --> 00:21:18,490
玩家是来赢赌场钱的…
Since the players are looking to beat the casino...

356
00:21:19,920 --> 00:21:22,290
庄家得看好玩家…
the dealers are watching the players...

357
00:21:24,260 --> 00:21:26,500
收付赌注得看好庄家…
the boxmen are watching the dealers...

358
00:21:27,130 --> 00:21:29,510
管场的注意着收付赌注的人…
the floormen are watching the boxmen...

359
00:21:30,100 --> 00:21:32,670
赌区经理看着管场的…
the pit bosses are watching the floormen...

360
00:21:32,930 --> 00:21:35,770
值班经理看着赌区经理…
the shift bosses are watching the pit bosses...

361
00:21:35,850 --> 00:21:38,640
赌场经理看着值班经理…
the casino manager is watching the shift bosses...

362
00:21:38,770 --> 00:21:40,930
我则看着赌场经理…
I'm watching the casino manager...

363
00:21:41,110 --> 00:21:44,310
而监视照相机看着我们大家
and the eye in the sky is watching us all.

364
00:21:48,700 --> 00:21:50,740
另外，还有十多个家伙…
Plus, we had a dozen guys...

365
00:21:50,870 --> 00:21:54,040
大多以前都是老千 他们知道所有的骗术
most of them ex-cheats, who knew every trick in the house.

366
00:22:15,020 --> 00:22:16,100
好啊！
Yes!

367
00:22:16,770 --> 00:22:19,530
-非常好 -我就跟你说我今天很旺
-Very nice. -I told you I was hot tonight.

368
00:22:31,170 --> 00:22:32,620
好样的
Looking good.

369
00:22:33,210 --> 00:22:35,080
来吧，为了金吉儿，快
MAN: Let's go. This is for Ginger.

370
00:22:35,210 --> 00:22:37,200
一百赌你没老A
MAN: Let me have $100 on your hard 10.

371
00:22:38,260 --> 00:22:39,340
谢谢
Thank you.

372
00:22:40,390 --> 00:22:41,580
来吧
MAN: Here we go now.

373
00:22:52,860 --> 00:22:54,900
-对不起 -骰子
-Oh, I'm sorry. -The dice.

374
00:22:56,900 --> 00:22:58,700
多谢
Thank you very much.

375
00:23:00,580 --> 00:23:02,030
多谢你
I appreciate that.

376
00:23:02,740 --> 00:23:05,280
保重，史蒂夫 要冒险啊，开快车
Take care, Steve. Take chances, drive fast.

377
00:23:06,460 --> 00:23:08,910
这一百给你，甜心 多谢你赏光
This $100 is for you, love. Thanks for your time.

378
00:23:10,550 --> 00:23:12,370
-快点 -怎么了？
-Come on. -What's the matter?

379
00:23:13,380 --> 00:23:16,090
我帮你赚了不少，我要我的份
I made a lot of money for you, I want my cut.

380
00:23:16,220 --> 00:23:18,010
什么钱？我看到你偷钱
What money? I've seen you stealing.

381
00:23:18,140 --> 00:23:20,510
“什么钱？” 你看看这堆筹码
"What money?" Look at the stack of chips.

382
00:23:20,640 --> 00:23:22,850
-我要我的一半 -我观察你一夜了
GINGER: I want my half. GAMBLER: I've watched you.

383
00:23:22,930 --> 00:23:25,310
-我要我的钱 -你皮包里全是熟筹码
-I want my money. -Your bag is full of chips.

384
00:23:25,440 --> 00:23:27,890
-我才没偷你的东西 -滚吧！
GINGER: I didn't steal anything from you. GAMBLER: Get lost!

385
00:23:28,820 --> 00:23:30,270
-滚吧？ -没错！
GINGER: Get lost? GAMBLER: Yes!

386
00:23:30,740 --> 00:23:33,060
-这怎么样呢？ -别这样！
-Well, how about that? -Come on!

387
00:24:24,210 --> 00:24:27,330
真酷，让我一见钟情
SAM: What a move. I fell in love right there.

388
00:24:27,470 --> 00:24:31,000
但在赌城，像金吉儿这样的女孩 得花上大钱
But in Vegas, for a girl like Ginger, love costs money.

389
00:24:36,810 --> 00:24:38,520
我去补个妆
I'm gonna go powder my nose.

390
00:24:49,740 --> 00:24:52,910
-金吉儿的人生目标是钱 -马上回来
SAM: Ginger's mission in life was money. I'll be right back.

391
00:24:53,040 --> 00:24:55,080
-待会见，金吉儿 -多谢你
DOORMAN: See you. GINGER: Thanks for asking.

392
00:24:55,170 --> 00:24:56,870
她在赌场可是皇后
SAM: She was a queen around the casino.

393
00:24:57,000 --> 00:25:00,420
她召来大赌客 并也帮他们花大钱
She brought in high rollers and helped them spend a lot of money.

394
00:25:00,800 --> 00:25:03,000
-你好 -嘿，金吉儿，你好吗？
-Hello. -Hey, Ginger. How you doing?

395
00:25:03,090 --> 00:25:05,800
好得很，一点小意思 你帮我搞定了吗？
GINGER: Great. You might have something for me. Got me covered?

396
00:25:06,850 --> 00:25:09,140
-非常感谢 -自己保重喔
GINGER: Thank you. VALET: Take care of yourself.

397
00:25:09,220 --> 00:25:11,300
我有些幸运丸给你，安迪
I got some lucky pills for you, Andy.

398
00:25:11,940 --> 00:25:14,640
谁不想要金吉儿？ 她是城里名声最响亮…
SAM: Who didn't want her? She was one of the best known...

399
00:25:14,770 --> 00:25:17,860
也是道上最受欢迎的江湖人物
best liked and most respected hustlers in town.

400
00:25:21,780 --> 00:25:24,150
像她这么聪明的玩家 可以让男人…
Smart hustlers like her could keep a guy awake...

401
00:25:24,240 --> 00:25:26,700
两三天不睡 然后再让他一文不名的…
for two or three days before sending him home broke...

402
00:25:26,790 --> 00:25:28,910
回到老婆与银行审查主任身边
to the little woman and his bank examiners.

403
00:25:44,220 --> 00:25:45,600
有找钱吗？
Any change?

404
00:25:46,770 --> 00:25:50,270
我回来时小赌了几把
Oh, I hit a few games on the way back.

405
00:25:51,610 --> 00:25:54,690
那根本是胡扯 她把钱收起来了
SAM: But that was all bullshit. She just pocketed the cash.

406
00:25:57,570 --> 00:25:59,450
-你今天好吗？ -不错啊
GINGER: How you doing tonight? CASHlER: Good.

407
00:25:59,570 --> 00:26:01,120
-你呢？ -衰死了
CASHlER: How are you? GINGER: Beat.

408
00:26:01,240 --> 00:26:04,110
-金吉儿洞悉玩家们的习性 -给你一百
SAM: Ginger had the hustlers' code. GINGER: Take one for you.

409
00:26:04,960 --> 00:26:07,830
-多谢 -她懂得如何买通他人
CASHlER: Thank you. SAM: She knew how to take care of people.

410
00:26:07,960 --> 00:26:10,030
这就是赌城的座右铭
That's what Vegas is all about.

411
00:26:10,170 --> 00:26:12,620
-六千八百元 -谢啦
CASHlER: $6,800. GINGER: Thanks.

412
00:26:12,760 --> 00:26:15,290
-这里是讲究回扣的城市 -晚安
SAM: It's kickback city. GINGER: Have a good night.

413
00:26:21,180 --> 00:26:23,090
她罩庄家…
SAM: She took care of the dealers...

414
00:26:23,270 --> 00:26:25,510
赌区经理，管场经理…
pit bosses, floor managers...

415
00:26:25,900 --> 00:26:28,350
但尤其关照停车小弟…
but, mostly, the valet parkers...

416
00:26:28,440 --> 00:26:31,730
他们能帮你找到任何东西 也能帮你解决任何事
the guys who could get you anything and take care of anything.

417
00:26:31,860 --> 00:26:33,570
金吉儿搞定了停车的…
Ginger took care of the parkers...

418
00:26:33,700 --> 00:26:37,150
他们搞定警卫 而警卫会摆平警察…
who took care of the security guards, who took care of the cops...

419
00:26:37,280 --> 00:26:39,660
-让她可继续开工 -我今晚需要那东西
who let her operate. I need that stuff tonight.

420
00:26:40,000 --> 00:26:42,240
-没问题 -你真好
VALET: No problem. GINGER: You are a doll.

421
00:26:42,620 --> 00:26:44,870
停车赚的钱多到…
SAM: The valet parking job was such a money-maker...

422
00:26:44,960 --> 00:26:48,160
得买通酒店经理才能排上空缺
they had to pay off the hotel manager just to get the concession.

423
00:26:50,170 --> 00:26:52,380
不过有一点我不懂…
But one thing I didn't understand...

424
00:26:52,510 --> 00:26:54,970
她将一切都控制的好好的…
was that she had everything under control...

425
00:26:55,140 --> 00:26:57,840
却被她那拉皮条的男友 莱丝特戴蒙德吃得死死的
except for her old pimp boyfriend, Lester Diamond.

426
00:26:57,980 --> 00:27:00,220
我得顾到其他人，我的搭挡们
I got other people in this. I got partners.

427
00:27:01,520 --> 00:27:05,220
在这事上有我罩你，知道吗？
I'm looking out for you in this thing, okay?

428
00:27:05,480 --> 00:27:09,180
你将获你应得的 而且第一个拿到，好吗？
You'll get yours back, and you'll get it back first. Okay?

429
00:27:09,320 --> 00:27:11,530
-好的 -你去哪儿了？
-All right. -Where you going?

430
00:27:12,830 --> 00:27:14,570
你在哪儿？ 你又飘走了
Where are you? You're in that place.

431
00:27:14,660 --> 00:27:16,570
-我在这儿 -不，你不在
-I'm here. -No, you're not.

432
00:27:16,710 --> 00:27:17,740
你在哪？
Where are you?

433
00:27:19,830 --> 00:27:21,380
我永远在你身边
I'm always here for you.

434
00:27:22,920 --> 00:27:24,960
-真的 -是啊
-You are. -I am.

435
00:27:26,010 --> 00:27:28,550
我所认识的金吉儿 根本不会多看这怪胎一眼
SAM: The Ginger I knew wouldn't even look at this creep.

436
00:27:30,010 --> 00:27:31,670
-祝你好运 -是啊
-Good luck. -Yeah.

437
00:27:32,010 --> 00:27:33,720
他是个老千，专作假牌…
SAM: He was a moocher, a card cheat...

438
00:27:33,850 --> 00:27:36,520
老在高尔夫俱乐部招摇撞骗 一个瘪三…
a country club golf hustler, a scumbag...

439
00:27:36,980 --> 00:27:39,520
-为了几块钱追着牙医屁股跑 -小心点
-chasing dentists for a few bucks. -Careful.

440
00:27:39,690 --> 00:27:42,020
他永远都没钱，永远都有藉口
SAM: He was always broke. He always had a story.

441
00:27:42,150 --> 00:27:44,190
不知为何，她却拒绝不了他
Somehow, she could never turn him down.

442
00:27:44,530 --> 00:27:47,820
在金吉儿眼里，他只是运气不好
The way Ginger saw it was that he was just an unlucky guy.

443
00:27:48,030 --> 00:27:49,860
总得有人照顾他
Somebody had to take care of him.

444
00:27:50,490 --> 00:27:51,530
在老家
BACK HOME

445
00:27:51,620 --> 00:27:53,410
但尼奇可不需要人照顾
But nobody had to take care of Nicky.

446
00:27:53,540 --> 00:27:56,210
你找到现金的话 我们就跟你平分
You find any cash in there, we'll whack it up with you.

447
00:27:56,290 --> 00:27:58,500
他把自己照顾得太好了
SAM: He took care of himself only too well.

448
00:27:58,840 --> 00:28:01,380
这也是为什么老家的条子 都想抓他到案
That's why every badge back home wanted to nail him.

449
00:28:01,510 --> 00:28:05,130
我将这些都折得好好的 能不能放尊重点
I folded these things beautifully. I would appreciate a little respect.

450
00:28:05,390 --> 00:28:07,590
别看我，兄弟 我还得跟她同床共枕
Don't look at me, pal, I gotta live with her.

451
00:28:08,720 --> 00:28:11,430
就连去渡个假 他们在机场时都不放过他
SAM: Even after a vacation, they hassled him at the airport.

452
00:28:11,560 --> 00:28:14,270
法兰克玛雷诺在那儿等他 条子们也在
Frank Marino was there to meet him. So were the cops.

453
00:28:14,400 --> 00:28:16,110
他们想逮他…
They wanted to pinch him...

454
00:28:16,190 --> 00:28:18,730
-因为一宗在安特卫普的钻石窃案 -帮忙折吧
-for a diamond burglary in Antwerp. -Help me fold these.

455
00:28:18,820 --> 00:28:21,850
他们随时愿意嫁祸于他 不管是在哪儿发生什么事
SAM: They were ready to blame him for anything, no matter where.

456
00:28:22,320 --> 00:28:23,700
他们通常是对的
They were usually right.

457
00:28:24,740 --> 00:28:26,570
因为尼奇很喜欢混帮派
Because Nicky enjoyed being a gangster.

458
00:28:26,700 --> 00:28:29,030
他也不在乎有谁知道
And he didn't give a damn who knew it.

459
00:28:29,120 --> 00:28:31,580
看看，美极了
GINGER: There we go. Look at that. Beautiful!

460
00:28:32,750 --> 00:28:34,130
让我担心的是…
SAM: I mean that's what worried me...

461
00:28:34,250 --> 00:28:37,290
尼奇似乎要被派来拉斯维加斯
'cause it turns out, Nicky was about to be sent to Vegas.

462
00:28:37,420 --> 00:28:39,460
-好了，就这样 -还有
JENNlFER: All right, we're clear. NICKY: There's more.

463
00:28:41,260 --> 00:28:43,140
一定还有些卡在里面
NICKY: There's a couple stuck in there.

464
00:28:43,260 --> 00:28:45,090
-我告诉你都拿出来了 -快
-I'm telling you, they're out! -Come on.

465
00:28:45,220 --> 00:28:48,340
别急于辩护 可能还有些卡在你头发里
Don't get so defensive, it could be stuck in your hair.

466
00:28:50,270 --> 00:28:51,730
那是什么？
What's that?

467
00:28:52,610 --> 00:28:54,600
没有了，谢谢
There's no more. Thanks.

468
00:28:54,780 --> 00:28:57,610
我迫不及待想去拉斯维加斯
NICKY: I couldn't wait to get my hands on Vegas.

469
00:28:57,820 --> 00:29:00,490
但老大可不是送我去玩的
But the bosses didn't send me out to have a good time.

470
00:29:00,620 --> 00:29:03,620
他们要我去确保 没人找艾斯的麻烦
They sent me out to make sure that nobody fucked with Ace.

471
00:29:03,700 --> 00:29:06,240
也确保没人干扰每月的抽头
And nobody interfered with the fucking skim.

472
00:29:08,670 --> 00:29:10,040
-嘿 -你好吗？
-Hey. -Hey, how you doing?

473
00:29:11,130 --> 00:29:12,500
嘿，山姆
Hey, Sammy.

474
00:29:13,800 --> 00:29:16,500
-天呀，瞧瞧这地方 -不可思议
-Boy, look at this place. -Incredible.

475
00:29:17,300 --> 00:29:18,760
欢迎来赌城
SAM: Welcome to Vegas.

476
00:29:18,850 --> 00:29:20,420
-好样的，山姆 -不错吧
NICKY: Okay, Sammy. SAM: Something, huh?

477
00:29:21,810 --> 00:29:23,010
金吉儿
Ginger.

478
00:29:27,650 --> 00:29:29,810
靠，你都在这儿干嘛？
Holy shit. What've you been doing out here?

479
00:29:30,400 --> 00:29:31,560
甜心，过来
SAM: Honey, come here.

480
00:29:33,990 --> 00:29:36,480
这是珍妮佛与尼克 我的好朋友们
This is Jennifer and Nick. They're dear friends of mine.

481
00:29:36,580 --> 00:29:38,370
-你好，珍妮佛 -幸会
-Hi, Jennifer. -A pleasure.

482
00:29:40,660 --> 00:29:42,120
好样的，山姆
Okay, Sammy.

483
00:29:42,500 --> 00:29:45,120
晚餐后，我们让珍妮佛 与金吉儿一块儿…
SAM: After we ate, we left Jennifer and Ginger...

484
00:29:45,210 --> 00:29:46,790
我们俩则出去谈话
and we took a ride to talk.

485
00:29:47,130 --> 00:29:49,500
然后他对我丢了颗炸弹
And then, he hit me with it.

