00:39:14,860 --> 00:39:16,320
你不觉得是时候了？
Don't you think it's time?

650
00:39:16,860 --> 00:39:20,400
你对这些不厌烦吗？ 这边睡、那边混？
Aren't you getting tired of all this shit? Banging around, hustling around?

651
00:39:20,540 --> 00:39:23,700
-你想要妨碍我吗？ -我想给你更好的
-Are you trying to handicap me? -I'm gonna do you one better.

652
00:39:24,750 --> 00:39:26,120
我想娶你进门
I'm trying to marry you.

653
00:39:27,710 --> 00:39:28,910
你想嫁我吗？
SAM: You wanna marry me?

654
00:39:30,550 --> 00:39:32,010
我说真的
SAM: I'm serious.

655
00:39:34,550 --> 00:39:36,670
我想定下来，想有个家
I wanna settle down. I want a family.

656
00:39:36,850 --> 00:39:39,380
你找错人了，山姆
You got the wrong girl, Sam.

657
00:39:39,850 --> 00:39:42,060
我会是个好爸爸 你也将是个好妈妈
I'd be a good father, you'd be a good mother.

658
00:39:42,190 --> 00:39:43,510
你不知道我
You don't know me.

659
00:39:43,650 --> 00:39:46,180
你才认识我两、三个月 你了解什么？
You've known me two, three months. What do you know?

660
00:39:46,480 --> 00:39:48,520
我已经43岁了，我不想再等了
I'm 43 years old. I don't want to wait.

661
00:39:49,240 --> 00:39:52,320
我对你的了解深到 令我自己知道我非常爱你
I know you well enough to know that I really love you very much.

662
00:39:53,490 --> 00:39:55,650
你是我心目中最理想的人
I can't think of anybody better to be with.

663
00:39:56,330 --> 00:39:58,120
我不想再等了
I don't feel like waiting anymore.

664
00:40:01,000 --> 00:40:03,700
你见过很多婚姻美满的人吗？ 我可没见过
You know a lot of happily married people? 'Cause I don't.

665
00:40:05,340 --> 00:40:06,420
这我都懂
I know all that.

666
00:40:11,590 --> 00:40:12,710
我在乎你
I care about you.

667
00:40:14,060 --> 00:40:16,590
但我对你没有那种感觉
But I just don't have those kind of feelings for you.

668
00:40:19,400 --> 00:40:21,640
对不起，我并不爱你
I'm sorry. I'm not in love with you.

669
00:40:24,610 --> 00:40:26,570
-好的 -懂吗？
SAM: All right. GINGER: Understand?

670
00:40:28,740 --> 00:40:30,070
对不起
GINGER: I'm sorry.

671
00:40:30,910 --> 00:40:32,020
不…
No....

672
00:40:36,620 --> 00:40:38,000
那可以培养
That can grow.

673
00:40:38,130 --> 00:40:41,250
只要互相尊重 感情是可以培养的
As long as there's a mutual respect, that kind of thing can grow.

674
00:40:41,840 --> 00:40:44,710
我很现实，我可以接受
I'm realistic. I can accept that.

675
00:40:45,760 --> 00:40:47,470
爱到底是什么？
SAM: What is love anyway?

676
00:40:47,550 --> 00:40:50,170
不就是互相尊重 不就是一心一意
SAM: It's a mutual respect. It's a devotion.

677
00:40:50,310 --> 00:40:53,140
是一个人在乎另一个人
It's a caring from one person to another.

678
00:40:54,100 --> 00:40:57,350
若我们可以设立一个基础…
And if we could set up some kind of foundation...

679
00:40:58,150 --> 00:40:59,890
以相互尊重为底…
based on that mutual respect...

680
00:41:01,280 --> 00:41:03,980
我觉得迟早你会对我有情…
I feel that eventually you would care enough about me...

681
00:41:04,410 --> 00:41:05,860
这样我能接受
that I could live with that.

682
00:41:08,450 --> 00:41:09,950
若行不通的话…
If it doesn't work out...

683
00:41:10,330 --> 00:41:12,700
若行不通的话 那我怎么办？
if it doesn't play out, then what happens to me?

684
00:41:13,330 --> 00:41:16,000
我现在做得不错 往后会越来越好
I'm doing well now. I'm gonna do even better.

685
00:41:16,500 --> 00:41:18,050
不论如何…
So whatever happens...

686
00:41:18,670 --> 00:41:20,550
就算我们俩行不通…
if it doesn't work out between us...

687
00:41:20,670 --> 00:41:23,250
我都会确保你下半辈子的生活
I'll make sure you're okay for the rest of your life.

688
00:41:23,510 --> 00:41:25,500
尤其如果有了孩子…
If there are kids, especially...

689
00:41:26,180 --> 00:41:28,260
我会给你今生最好的照料
I'll take care of you better than you'd imagine.

690
00:41:28,390 --> 00:41:30,720
-你葫芦到底卖什么药？ -我都明讲了
GINGER: What are you pitching me? SAM: Just what I said.

691
00:41:32,060 --> 00:41:34,390
你下半辈子都不用愁
You'll be set up for the rest of your life.

692
00:41:34,980 --> 00:41:36,360
这我可保证
That I can promise you.

693
00:41:41,070 --> 00:41:42,350
要不要试试？
Want to take a chance?

694
00:41:52,460 --> 00:41:55,330
我娶金吉儿时就听过她的一切往事…
SAM: When I married Ginger, I knew all the stories...

695
00:41:55,460 --> 00:41:58,130
但我不在乎 我是山姆罗斯坦
but I didn't give a fuck. I'm Sam Rothstein, I said.

696
00:41:58,260 --> 00:41:59,340
我能改变她
I can change her.

697
00:42:01,970 --> 00:42:03,430
这是典型的艾斯
NICKY: It was typical Ace.

698
00:42:03,560 --> 00:42:06,810
他请了城里所有的大人物 他知道他们都会出席
He invited the biggest people in town. He knew they'd show.

699
00:42:06,940 --> 00:42:09,310
他知道他们都有求于他
He knew they all wanted something from him.

700
00:42:09,440 --> 00:42:12,640
艾斯绝对不可能不求回报 连金吉儿也不例外
With Ace, nobody ever got a free ride. Even Ginger.

701
00:42:12,780 --> 00:42:14,600
一切还是依他行事
With her, he still covered his bets.

702
00:42:14,740 --> 00:42:17,770
他们在结婚前得先有孩子
They had to have the baby first, before they could get married.

703
00:42:17,870 --> 00:42:20,360
他甚至还托我们帮忙看艾美几天…
He even made us watch Amy for a few days...

704
00:42:20,490 --> 00:42:21,950
好让他们去渡蜜月
when they went on their honeymoon.

705
00:42:22,040 --> 00:42:23,750
无所谓啊 我们爱死那孩子
I didn't mind, we loved the kid.

706
00:42:28,380 --> 00:42:29,840
你感到我的眼神？
LESTER: Can you feel my eyes on you?

707
00:42:31,590 --> 00:42:33,500
你感到我看透你的心吗？
Can you feel me look into your heart?

708
00:42:34,930 --> 00:42:37,090
你能感到我躺在你肚皮上吗？
Can you feel me in the pit of your stomach?

709
00:42:40,640 --> 00:42:42,100
你能在体内感受我？
Can you feel me in you?

710
00:42:44,190 --> 00:42:45,220
在心里？
In your heart?

711
00:42:48,230 --> 00:42:49,690
别等我过去
Don't make me come there.

712
00:42:50,950 --> 00:42:52,320
回答我
Answer me.

713
00:42:52,860 --> 00:42:54,240
我爱你
GINGER: [Crying] I love you.

714
00:42:54,450 --> 00:42:56,490
宝贝，你知道我也爱你吗？
Baby, do you know that I love you, too?

715
00:42:56,740 --> 00:42:58,740
-不，莱斯特 -你知道吗？
GINGER: No, Lester. LESTER: Do you know that?

716
00:42:58,830 --> 00:42:59,940
知道
GINGER: Yes.

717
00:43:00,290 --> 00:43:03,330
这是我目前能为自己做的 最好的事
This is the best thing I can do for my life right now.

718
00:43:03,460 --> 00:43:04,660
没错
That's right.

719
00:43:04,800 --> 00:43:06,540
所以会没事的
So it's going to be okay.

720
00:43:06,670 --> 00:43:07,870
你发誓？
Promise?

721
00:43:08,550 --> 00:43:10,840
我希望你幸福
I wish you all the luck in the world.

722
00:43:11,640 --> 00:43:13,710
-真的？ -是，我真的这么想
GINGER: You do? LESTER: Yeah, I do.

723
00:43:14,220 --> 00:43:17,090
这是你目前能做的最好的事
It's the best thing you can do right now.

724
00:43:17,690 --> 00:43:19,060
我说真的
I mean this.

725
00:43:19,310 --> 00:43:21,270
你生活会很安稳
You have real security.

726
00:43:21,520 --> 00:43:25,220
甜心，你将坐在赌城最有利的位子
Sweetheart, you're gonna be situated just right in Vegas.

727
00:43:25,320 --> 00:43:27,610
这对我们来说再好不过了
Come on. This is great for us.

728
00:43:28,110 --> 00:43:30,820
我会一直都在你身边的 我哪儿都不会去
I'm always gonna be here for you. I ain't going no place.

729
00:43:33,040 --> 00:43:34,580
我现在就在看着你
I'm looking at you right now.

730
00:43:35,830 --> 00:43:38,670
仿佛生平第一次见到你似的
I'm seeing you for the very first time, right this minute.

731
00:43:39,250 --> 00:43:41,160
我可听到我的心悸动
I'm saying I can feel my heart click.

732
00:43:42,300 --> 00:43:43,840
我看到你十四岁时
I see you 14 years old.

733
00:43:43,970 --> 00:43:46,090
我在见你的第一秒就看到你了
I see you the first second I ever saw you.

734
00:43:47,430 --> 00:43:49,880
我看到你，像匹长腿的小马儿…
I see you, long-legged little colt...

735
00:43:49,970 --> 00:43:52,130
还戴着蠢蠢的牙套
stupid braces on your teeth.

736
00:43:52,270 --> 00:43:55,550
-好吧 -我每次见你时都看到这些
Okay, then. LESTER: Every time I see you, that's what I see.

737
00:43:56,350 --> 00:43:58,640
再聊罗，再见
Talk to you later. Bye.

738
00:44:05,660 --> 00:44:07,570
-你还好吗？ -嗯
-You all right? -Yeah.

739
00:44:09,790 --> 00:44:10,990
为什么哭？
Why are you crying?

740
00:44:13,580 --> 00:44:14,700
我没有哭
I'm not crying.

741
00:44:20,420 --> 00:44:23,710
-别喝这么多了吧 -我没事
-Maybe you shouldn't drink so much. -I'm okay.

742
00:44:28,390 --> 00:44:29,930
希望你能理解
You just have to understand.

743
00:44:30,850 --> 00:44:33,610
我自小就跟莱斯特在一起
I've been with Lester since I was a kid.

744
00:44:36,030 --> 00:44:37,650
我只是想道别
I just wanted to say goodbye.

745
00:44:39,240 --> 00:44:40,400
我只是…
I just....

746
00:44:42,950 --> 00:44:44,740
我想我有权这样做
I think I have a right to do that.

747
00:44:48,370 --> 00:44:49,490
好吗？
GINGER: Okay?

748
00:44:49,620 --> 00:44:50,700
没关系
It's all right.

749
00:44:52,500 --> 00:44:54,380
你那段人生已经完结了
That part of your life is over with.

750
00:44:55,170 --> 00:44:56,960
-不是吗？ -是的
SAM: Right? GINGER: Yeah.

751
00:44:58,220 --> 00:44:59,330
你现在跟我
You're with me now.

752
00:45:01,050 --> 00:45:02,510
-是的 -不是吗？
-Yeah. -Right?

753
00:45:05,890 --> 00:45:07,800
-你确定吗？ -是的
SAM: You're sure? GINGER: Yeah.

754
00:45:15,530 --> 00:45:18,570
-要走了吗？我们回去吧 -好的
SAM: Want to go? Let's go back in. GINGER: Okay.

755
00:45:38,710 --> 00:45:40,080
很好
GINGER: It's great.

756
00:45:50,180 --> 00:45:53,340
都是我的东西，天呀
GINGER: It's all my stuff. Oh, my God.

757
00:45:54,140 --> 00:45:56,180
你把我的东西都带来了！
You brought all my stuff!

758
00:45:56,470 --> 00:45:57,750
我不能…
I can't....

759
00:45:59,390 --> 00:46:00,930
试试看，这是你的
Try it on. It's yours.

760
00:46:01,850 --> 00:46:03,100
别开玩笑了
You're kidding.

761
00:46:05,320 --> 00:46:06,510
我的天
My God.

762
00:46:07,400 --> 00:46:09,860
-是什么毛？ -是龙猫
-What is it? -It's chinchilla.

763
00:46:10,530 --> 00:46:11,990
好软喔
It's so soft.

764
00:46:13,320 --> 00:46:14,860
很好喔？
Nice, isn't it?

765
00:46:19,700 --> 00:46:21,450
从没有人对我这么好
No one's ever been so nice to me.

766
00:46:33,630 --> 00:46:35,010
我的老天！
GINGER: Oh, my God!

767
00:46:37,140 --> 00:46:40,420
我要是在同一天将它们全都戴上 会不会太过火啊？
Do you think it's too much if I wear these all on the same day?

768
00:46:40,520 --> 00:46:42,550
你想怎样就怎样
You can do whatever you want.

769
00:46:42,850 --> 00:46:45,340
我有没有实现我的诺言啊？
Do I keep my promises or do I keep my promises?

770
00:46:45,560 --> 00:46:48,430
你太好了 这些珠宝也不错
You're so wonderful. The jewelry's not so bad either.

771
00:46:48,570 --> 00:46:52,270
我们不应该把这些放在家里 应该摆到银行去
We shouldn't keep this in the house. We gotta put it in the bank.

772
00:46:52,440 --> 00:46:54,570
我不能留一副在家吗？
Come on. Can I keep this one in the house?

773
00:46:55,450 --> 00:46:56,690
仔细听好
Pay attention to me.

774
00:46:58,320 --> 00:47:00,480
我要告诉你一件重要的事
What I'm gonna tell you is very important.

775
00:47:01,450 --> 00:47:03,490
这全部都不算什么
All this stuff doesn't mean anything.

776
00:47:03,620 --> 00:47:05,990
钱财珠宝 如果没有信任就毫无意义
Money, this, doesn't mean anything without trust.

777
00:47:06,290 --> 00:47:08,500
我得要信任你到可将生命交给你
I have to be able to trust you with my life.

778
00:47:10,170 --> 00:47:14,210
洛杉矶

779
00:47:19,300 --> 00:47:23,000
总价值超过一百万的现金与珠宝 锁在赌城的银行里…
SAM: With over $1 million in cash and jewels tucked in a bank in Vegas...

780
00:47:23,100 --> 00:47:25,300
全归她所有 金吉儿非常有安全感
only for Ginger, she was secure and happy.

781
00:47:25,430 --> 00:47:26,680
她最爱那些
She loved that shit.

782
00:47:27,310 --> 00:47:30,930
但在我这行里 手上得有许多流动的现金
But a guy in my line of work has to have a lot of payoff cash around.

783
00:47:31,570 --> 00:47:34,100
贪污的条子与绑匪 他们都不收支票
Crooked cops and kidnappers, they don't take checks.

784
00:47:34,730 --> 00:47:36,770
考林先生，需要帮忙吗？
Need any help with that, Mr. Collins?

785
00:47:36,860 --> 00:47:39,350
所以我在洛杉矶的银行里 也摆了两百万…
SAM: So I put $2 million cash in a Los Angeles bank...

786
00:47:39,490 --> 00:47:42,280
用考林先生与夫人的名义
under the name of Mr. and Mrs. Tom Collins.

787
00:47:42,740 --> 00:47:45,530
这纯粹是我个人的赎金与保金
This was strictly my shakedown and kidnapping money.

788
00:47:50,120 --> 00:47:54,500
因为在我最需要这笔钱时 我不是蹲在牢里就是被关在衣柜…
Since I'd be in jail or locked in a closet when I needed the money most...

789
00:47:54,670 --> 00:47:59,300
所以我将这笔钱唯一的钥匙 给了金吉儿好让我能保命
I gave Ginger the only key to the cash that could get me back alive.

790
00:48:11,940 --> 00:48:13,730
这是签名卡
This is just a signature card.

791
00:48:15,480 --> 00:48:17,810
她签了之后就会是世上…
Once she signs, she'll be the only person...

792
00:48:17,940 --> 00:48:21,150
唯一可以开保险箱的人 连我都开启不了？
to have total access to the box, no one else, including myself?

793
00:48:21,490 --> 00:48:23,810
是的，这是你的要求
BANKER: That's right. That's the way you wanted it.

794
00:48:24,990 --> 00:48:26,620
山姆，我问你个问题
Sam, let me ask you a question.

795
00:48:27,790 --> 00:48:29,490
你一定很信任你老婆
You must really trust your wife.

796
00:48:32,540 --> 00:48:34,080
是啊，怎么啦？
Sure I do. Why?

797
00:48:35,130 --> 00:48:37,410
很好啊，只是很少见
It's good. It's just unusual.

798
00:48:37,880 --> 00:48:40,420
实不相瞒 我有很多客户都不信任
To tell you the truth, so many of my clients don't.

799
00:48:56,020 --> 00:48:58,730
将金吉儿还有钱的事解决后 我安心多了
SAM: With Ginger and the money in place, I felt covered.

800
00:48:58,900 --> 00:49:01,390
为了安全起见，我又将头衔…
To play it safe, I switched job titles again...

801
00:49:01,490 --> 00:49:04,690
换成餐饮董事
and made myself Food and Beverage Director.

802
00:49:04,820 --> 00:49:07,310
这样一来就没人可以 为执照的事找我麻烦
This way nobody would bother me about a license.

803
00:49:07,490 --> 00:49:09,450
赌城对我来说像是个梦
Vegas was like a dream for me.

804
00:49:09,580 --> 00:49:12,410
问题是尼奇也梦想着 他自己的赌城
Trouble was Nicky was dreaming of his own kind of Vegas.

805
00:49:12,500 --> 00:49:15,750
我将钱放出，每天三分利
NICKY: I put money out on the street charging three points a week.

806
00:49:15,870 --> 00:49:16,990
庄家高利贷
Juice to the dealers.

807
00:49:17,130 --> 00:49:20,490
-别逼我们找上门 -你不会需要这样的
-Don't make us look for you. -You won't have to look for me.

808
00:49:20,590 --> 00:49:22,460
多谢了，尼奇
I appreciate it. Thanks, Nicky.

809
00:49:22,590 --> 00:49:25,130
他们不是烂赌鬼就是烂毒鬼
NICKY: They were degenerate gamblers, coke freaks.

810
00:49:25,260 --> 00:49:28,630
没多久，坦吉乐一半的庄家 都在我手掌心里
In no time, I had half the dealers in the Tangiers in my pocket.

811
00:49:29,350 --> 00:49:33,890
下一步，我开始出千骗大赌客的钱
Then, the next thing I did, I started busting out high-stakes poker players.

812
00:49:34,020 --> 00:49:35,480
好明显
SAM: It was so obvious.

813
00:49:35,600 --> 00:49:38,720
尼奇所有的小把戏 全都是靠手势
All of Nicky's half-assed mechanics, they were signal-happy.

814
00:49:38,860 --> 00:49:40,510
我下五百
I'm gonna open for $500.

815
00:49:40,650 --> 00:49:42,140
互相打手势
SAM: Signaling back and forth.

816
00:49:46,450 --> 00:49:49,150
尼奇以为没人注意到他 但是他错了
Nicky thought nobody was watching him. But he was wrong.

817
00:49:49,370 --> 00:49:51,900
我不想要那些探员在我的地盘
I didn't want any of those agents near my place.

818
00:49:52,030 --> 00:49:54,490
-四条A -我不相信
-Four aces. -I can't believe this.

819
00:49:55,830 --> 00:49:58,370
我唯一的运气好像就是手气背
GAMBLER 2: If I didn't have bad luck, I wouldn't have any luck.

820
