他们是探员，法兰克 来看看
They're fucking agents, Frankie. Look at this.

1730
01:41:32,460 --> 01:41:35,000
他们盯尼奇打高尔夫盯到…
SAM: The Feds were watching Nicky play golf for so long...

1731
01:41:35,170 --> 01:41:36,370
飞机没油
they ran out of gas.

1732
01:41:37,920 --> 01:41:40,670
还真是我需要的 就在委员会面前
Just what I needed, right in front of the control board.

1733
01:41:45,890 --> 01:41:47,710
赌一百看谁先打到飞机
$100, whoever hits the plane.

1734
01:41:50,850 --> 01:41:55,230
祸不单行，随后就看到派斯康 堪萨斯市的老二
SAM: If things weren't bad enough... in comes Piscano, the Kansas City underboss.

1735
01:41:55,320 --> 01:41:58,810
在堪萨斯市收皮箱的那家超市 就是他开的
He ran the grocery store in Kansas City where they brought the suitcases.

1736
01:41:58,940 --> 01:42:02,150
又在为皮箱的事吵了 你知道这代表什么吗？
Fighting over those suitcases again. You know what that means?

1737
01:42:02,280 --> 01:42:05,820
我又得去拉斯维加斯了 又要花我好几千
I gotta take another trip to Vegas. It's gonna cost me another couple grand.

1738
01:42:05,950 --> 01:42:07,450
他和他姐夫一起开店…
SAM: He ran it with his brother-in-law...

1739
01:42:07,540 --> 01:42:11,910
但他大多都在跟他姐夫与岳母 抱怨他去赌城的事
but he mostly complained about his trips to Vegas to his brother-in-law and mother.

1740
01:42:12,040 --> 01:42:15,160
你得表明态度 要不然他们当你是病猫
You gotta lay down the law, or they'll make a fool out of you.

1741
01:42:15,590 --> 01:42:19,120
我全记下来了，他妈的每一分一毛
I write it all down. Every fucking nickel goes down.

1742
01:42:19,260 --> 01:42:22,920
-你是怎么了？ -全都在这儿
-What's the matter with you? -Everything's here.

1743
01:42:23,010 --> 01:42:25,000
-你何时开始这样讲话？ -抱歉
-Since when do you talk like that? -I'm sorry.

1744
01:42:25,140 --> 01:42:29,640
南斯要是找我麻烦 我就将他的眼挖出来
Nance gives me trouble, I'll take the eyes out of his freaking head.

1745
01:42:29,730 --> 01:42:32,050
-又来了 -我没骂粗话
-Again. -I didn't curse, I said, "freaking head."

1746
01:42:32,190 --> 01:42:33,350
-够了 -抱歉
-That's enough. -I'm sorry.

1747
01:42:33,480 --> 01:42:35,520
接下来发生的事 简直是出乎意料
SAM: What happens next, you can't believe it.

1748
01:42:35,780 --> 01:42:38,560
谁会想到联邦调查局 会在里面装窃听器…
Who'd believe the FBI had a wire in the place...

1749
01:42:38,700 --> 01:42:41,360
为了调查很久以前的一桩命案…
looking for information about some old homicide...

1750
01:42:41,450 --> 01:42:44,780
为了一个不知在何时 也不知为何事被干掉的人
about some guy who was whacked out God knows when over God knows what?

1751
01:42:44,870 --> 01:42:47,870
你怎么阻止拿皮箱的人 拿走他想要的？
What prevents him with the suitcases from taking what he wants?

1752
01:42:48,000 --> 01:42:50,250
南斯从坦吉乐拿了两口箱子回来
Nance brings back two suitcases from the Tangiers.

1753
01:42:50,250 --> 01:42:51,910
若其实有三箱或四箱呢？
What about three or four?

1754
01:42:52,040 --> 01:42:54,910
我们没有人在计算室里看着 那是法律
We've got nobody in the room to watch. That's the law.

1755
01:42:55,050 --> 01:42:58,660
我们甚至连计算室都进不去
We can't even go into the count room to watch our money.

1756
01:42:58,760 --> 01:43:03,340
他有他的人在里面 他们搞不好根本是一伙的
He's got his people in there. They could all be in on it together.

1757
01:43:04,100 --> 01:43:07,260
若我知道是葛林干的 我会埋了那王八蛋
I'll find out. If it's Green himself, I'll bury that bastard.

1758
01:43:07,390 --> 01:43:09,930
我从就不相信他 我后脑都有眼睛
I never trusted him. I got eyes behind my head.

1759
01:43:10,060 --> 01:43:11,770
他们信任那浑蛋，我可不
They trust that scumbag. I don't.

1760
01:43:11,860 --> 01:43:14,140
我该给他们一人一铲
I'll hit the two of them in the head with a shovel.

1761
01:43:14,280 --> 01:43:15,310
冷静点
MA: Take it easy.

1762
01:43:15,440 --> 01:43:18,190
妈，抱歉 但他们一直跟我玩阴的
Ma, I'm sorry. They're beating me left and right.

1763
01:43:18,320 --> 01:43:20,650
-抱歉，我很生气 -我知道，可是够了
ARTIE: I'm sorry. I'm upset. I know, but that's enough.

1764
01:43:20,740 --> 01:43:23,910
你也知道他们在对我做什么 我受不了了
You know what they're doing to me. I can't take this no more.

1765
01:43:24,040 --> 01:43:27,650
-冷静，别心脏病发 -我知道，我太气了
MA: Take it easy. You'll get a heart attack. ARTIE: I know. I'm too upset.

1766
01:43:28,920 --> 01:43:31,070
该死的是，他们听得一清二楚…
SAM: The damn thing is, they hear all this stuff...

1767
01:43:31,210 --> 01:43:34,460
关于拉斯维加斯，赌场还有皮箱…
about Las Vegas, casinos, and suitcases...

1768
01:43:34,590 --> 01:43:36,080
玩完了
and that's it.

1769
01:43:41,720 --> 01:43:44,470
全都是从我口袋里掏 我得付钱
ARTIE: Everything's coming out of my pocket. I gotta pay.

1770
01:43:45,890 --> 01:43:47,470
你相信有这么巧吗？
SAM: Would you believe this could happen?

1771
01:43:47,600 --> 01:43:48,800
华府

1772
01:43:48,980 --> 01:43:50,850
我是来赚钱的，不是亏钱
ARTIE: I'm in this to make money, not lose it.

1773
01:43:50,980 --> 01:43:54,680
全国每个联邦调查局探员 都张大了耳朵
SAM: Every FBI man across the country had their ears open now.

1774
01:43:54,820 --> 01:43:58,100
要将事情办好就得靠自己
ARTIE: If you want something done right you gotta do it yourself.

1775
01:43:58,870 --> 01:44:02,700
派司康这家伙 几乎搞砸了所有人的生活
SAM: Piscano, this guy, basically sunk the whole world.

1776
01:44:03,830 --> 01:44:06,150
有些好的就有些坏的
MA: There are some that are good and some that are bad.

1777
01:44:06,790 --> 01:44:07,740
1980年

1778
01:44:07,880 --> 01:44:09,700
主席先生 委员会的同仁…
COUNSELOR: Members of the Commission...

1779
01:44:09,840 --> 01:44:11,710
今天罗斯坦先生很荣幸能在这儿
Mr. Rothstein is pleased to be here today.

1780
01:44:11,840 --> 01:44:14,210
当那天终于来时 我已准备好了
SAM: When the day finally came, I was ready.

1781
01:44:14,300 --> 01:44:18,080
我自信满满的认为 我只需要呈上我的案件
I felt so confident that all I had to do was present my case.

1782
01:44:18,220 --> 01:44:22,720
我们拥有文件，其中一份是由 一位退休的联邦探员写的…
COUNSELOR: We have documents, one of which is a report by retired FBl agents...

1783
01:44:22,810 --> 01:44:26,090
上头清楚的记载罗斯坦先生 并未触犯任何法律
which completely absolves Mr. Rothstein from any wrongdoing.

1784
01:44:26,230 --> 01:44:29,680
-律师，在你继续前… -我要将这呈为…
-Counselor, before you continue... -I want to have this marked....

1785
01:44:29,820 --> 01:44:33,980
本委员会针对是否应 驳回罗斯坦的申请书在此动议
...this Commission acts on a motion denying the Rothstein application.

1786
01:44:34,070 --> 01:44:36,560
-驳回？ -有人赞成驳回吗？
COUNSELOR: Denying? SENATOR: Do I hear a motion seconded?

1787
01:44:37,200 --> 01:44:38,860
主席先生，我赞成
Mr. Chairman, I second the motion.

1788
01:44:38,990 --> 01:44:40,620
还有赞同票吗？
Do I have a vote on the motion?

1789
01:44:40,740 --> 01:44:41,780
同意！
-Aye! -Aye!

1790
01:44:43,210 --> 01:44:45,160
同意票获胜，听证会结束
The ayes have it. This hearing is adjourned.

1791
01:44:45,290 --> 01:44:48,460
-开什么玩笑 -什么叫结束？
-You have to be kidding. -Adjourned? What do you mean?

1792
01:44:49,250 --> 01:44:51,600
议员，你答应我一场听证会的
Senator, you promised me a hearing.

1793
01:44:51,610 --> 01:44:53,800
你连联邦调查局的报告都没看
You didn't even look at the FBl reports.

1794
01:44:54,050 --> 01:44:56,950
你来坦吉乐作客时
When you were my guest at the Tangiers Hotel,

1795
01:44:56,960 --> 01:44:58,930
不是答应我会有公平的听证会？
didn't you promise me a fair hearing?

1796
01:44:59,310 --> 01:45:00,720
-我从未是你的客人
SENATOR: I was never your guest.

1797
01:45:00,720 --> 01:45:02,840
-不是我的客人？我没招待过你？
SAM: Never my guest? I never comped you?

1798
01:45:02,980 --> 01:45:05,260
难道我一个月 没有最少招待你三次？
I don't comp you at least three times a month?

1799
01:45:05,400 --> 01:45:07,680
我现在回答这个问题
I'd like to answer that at this time.

1800
01:45:07,820 --> 01:45:11,100
罗斯坦先生的反应很常见 他在撒谎
Mr. Rothstein is being very typical to this point. He's lying.

1801
01:45:11,190 --> 01:45:15,110
我唯一一次去过坦吉乐 就是巴尼葛林斯坦那次晚宴
The only time I was at the Tangiers was a dinner with Barney Greenstein.

1802
01:45:15,240 --> 01:45:17,910
-我当时在场吗？ -你四处周旋着
Was I at the dinner? SENATOR: You were wandering around.

1803
01:45:18,030 --> 01:45:21,070
-我在场吗？ -你四处周旋
SAM: Was I at that dinner? SENATOR: You were wandering.

1804
01:45:21,160 --> 01:45:24,160
-你在室内 -我在室内？
SENATOR: You were in the building. SAM: I was in the building?

1805
01:45:24,290 --> 01:45:26,010
你很清楚我在那儿
You know damn well I was there.

1806
01:45:26,010 --> 01:45:28,500
你向我保证会有公正的听证会
You swore I would have a fair hearing.

1807
01:45:29,090 --> 01:45:31,160
没有吗？
Did you not?

1808
01:45:32,880 --> 01:45:36,130
至少承认说我那天在场 这总可以了吧
Tell me I was at least at the dinner. Allow me that much.

1809
01:45:36,850 --> 01:45:39,340
-至少也得说我在场吧！ -是，你在
SAM: Give me that much at least! SENATOR: Yes, you were.

1810
01:45:39,430 --> 01:45:42,140
多谢你没说我是骗子 你这个狗东西
Thanks for not calling me a liar, you son of a bitch.

1811
01:45:44,400 --> 01:45:47,770
一场例行的听证会 在昨晚成了一场闹剧…
A routine licensing hearing turned into bedlam yesterday...

1812
01:45:47,900 --> 01:45:51,600
当抢眼的坦吉乐高层 山姆“艾斯”罗斯坦…
when the flamboyant Tangiers Casino executive, Sam "Ace" Rothstein...

1813
01:45:51,700 --> 01:45:54,570
指控赌博游乐委员会高官贪污
accused top gaming officials of corruption.

1814
01:45:54,660 --> 01:45:57,530
你在我的旅馆接受招待 并答应我会有公平的听证会
...promised me a fair hearing when you were comped at my hotel?

1815
01:45:57,660 --> 01:46:00,860
你还要求将你的帐单挂公帐
And you asked for copies of your bill to put on your expense account.

1816
01:46:01,000 --> 01:46:04,250
当赌博游乐执照被驳回时大吼大叫…
In a wild outburst that followed his gaming license denial...

1817
01:46:04,380 --> 01:46:06,580
-狗屁！ -罗斯坦与好几名…
Bullshit! ...Rothstein followed several...

1818
01:46:06,710 --> 01:46:10,160
错愕的委员到走道 并持续着他的指控…
stunned commissioners into the hallway where he continued his harangue...

1819
01:46:10,260 --> 01:46:12,750
直到他的律师与朋友劝他离开
until his own lawyers and friends urged him to leave.

1820
01:46:12,890 --> 01:46:17,050
你有过去，我也有过去 我的不见得比你的糟糕
You have a past. I have a past. My past is no worse than yours.

1821
01:46:17,140 --> 01:46:19,890
你们还自以为有权去判决别人！
You guys think you have the right to pass judgment!

1822
01:46:20,020 --> 01:46:23,100
被怀疑长期无照管理坦吉乐…
NEWSREADER: Long suspected of running Tangiers without a license...

1823
01:46:23,230 --> 01:46:27,690
昨天的听证会本是要决议 像罗斯坦如此背景的人…
yesterday's hearing was to determine if someone with Rothstein's history...

1824
01:46:27,820 --> 01:46:30,650
是否有资格正式在赌博游乐界 担任如此高的职位
was qualified to officially hold a top gaming post.

1825
01:46:30,780 --> 01:46:32,940
罗斯坦玩完了 王八伪君子！
REMO: Fucking hypocrites!

1826
01:46:33,530 --> 01:46:36,740
-他现在怎么办？ -我不知道
-What the hell's he gonna do now? -I don't know.

1827
01:46:37,120 --> 01:46:38,490
他在干嘛？
What's he doing?

1828
01:46:38,870 --> 01:46:41,710
他也知道他大吼大叫的那群人 都是我们的朋友
He knows all those guys he yelled at are friends of ours.

1829
01:46:41,790 --> 01:46:44,000
他是怎么了，搞得一团糟？
What's the matter with him, making all this mess?

1830
01:46:44,130 --> 01:46:46,500
他或许可以用另一个头衔管事
Maybe he could run things with another job title.

1831
01:46:46,630 --> 01:46:49,090
这不是最好的 但我们又能如何呢？
Won't be the best, but what are we gonna do?

1832
01:46:49,340 --> 01:46:51,240
他不论管什么，都得安静点
REMO: However he runs things, it's gotta be quiet.

1833
01:46:51,340 --> 01:46:53,590
让他躲到楼上办公室去
Let him hide upstairs in the office.

1834
01:46:53,720 --> 01:46:55,760
说他是工友，我不在乎
Say he's a janitor. I don't give a shit.

1835
01:46:55,970 --> 01:47:00,880
但拜托，不管他做什么 都得低调点
But please, whatever job he takes, make sure it's something quiet.

1836
01:47:09,910 --> 01:47:11,280
各位先生与女士…
ANNOUNCER: [On TV] Ladies and gentlemen...

1837
01:47:11,370 --> 01:47:14,200
坦吉乐大饭店 非常荣幸能为您介绍…
the Tangiers Hotel proudly presents the all-new...

1838
01:47:14,330 --> 01:47:17,080
山姆罗斯坦秀，   《艾斯的单人牌》
Sam Rothstein show, Aces High.

1839
01:47:17,160 --> 01:47:18,160
艾斯的单人牌

1840
01:47:20,960 --> 01:47:23,830
今晚，从最新的球赛赌区 现场实况转播…
Tonight, taped live from the all-new sports book...

1841
01:47:23,920 --> 01:47:26,630
我们为您带来《艾斯的单人牌》的 首次演出…
we present the premiere showing of Aces High...

1842
01:47:27,050 --> 01:47:29,500
连同莎夏西门诺夫交响乐团…
with the Sasha Semenoff Orchestra...

1843
01:47:30,840 --> 01:47:33,300
与山姆罗斯坦舞群！
and the Sam Rothstein dancers!

1844
01:47:35,180 --> 01:47:39,930
罗斯坦先生是位职业赌徒 也是全美最棒的美式足球下注者
Mr. Rothstein is a professional gambler and the best U.S. football handicapper.

1845
01:47:40,230 --> 01:47:44,770
一位能带领你进入 真正的拉斯维加斯的人
A man who will take you inside the real Las Vegas as no one has ever done before.

1846
01:47:45,360 --> 01:47:49,610
现在让我们欢迎 坦吉乐赌场新的娱乐董事…
Now, the new entertainment director of the Tangiers Hotel Casino...

1847
01:47:49,910 --> 01:47:51,610
山姆罗斯坦先生
Mr. Sam Rothstein.

1848
01:48:01,000 --> 01:48:05,250
欢迎来到山姆罗斯坦秀 很高兴你们能参与
Welcome to the Sam Rothstein show. We're happy to have you here this evening.

1849
01:48:05,510 --> 01:48:08,000
我左边的这位小姐是特茹蒂…
The young lady to my left is Trudy...

1850
01:48:08,470 --> 01:48:11,630
她是我们巴黎秀新的首席舞者
who is a lead new dancer in our fabulous show from Paris.

1851
01:48:11,850 --> 01:48:14,140
我们今晚的第一位来宝…
Our first guest this evening...

1852
01:48:15,560 --> 01:48:16,890
法兰克艾华伦
is Frankie Avalon.

1853
01:48:22,820 --> 01:48:26,190
-看好他 -我有个大家庭
PAT: Keep an eye on him. FRANKIE: I've got a large family.

1854
01:48:26,280 --> 01:48:30,660
-你有几个孩子？ -我很自豪的说，八个
SAM: How many kids do you have? I'm very proud to say, eight children.

1855
01:48:34,000 --> 01:48:37,660
-太了不起了 -没什么，是我的荣幸
-That's amazing. -There's nothing to it. It was my pleasure.

1856
01:48:39,380 --> 01:48:40,490
别这样
PHILIP: Ace, don't do it.

1857
01:48:45,510 --> 01:48:46,670
天啊
Jesus.

1858
01:48:47,430 --> 01:48:48,920
他在耍杂技！
He's juggling!

1859
01:48:49,180 --> 01:48:52,710
我们别对县辅导 派特委布太认真
SAM: Let's not take County Commissioner Pat Webb too seriously.

1860
01:48:53,180 --> 01:48:56,770
我最近本想邀他在节目上辩论的 但是他拒绝了
I recently challenged him to a debate on this program, and he declined.

1861
01:48:56,940 --> 01:48:58,930
你在担心什么呢，派特？
What are you worried about, Pat?

1862
01:48:59,030 --> 01:49:01,150
你不需要事先给我问题
You don't have to send me any questions.

1863
01:49:02,190 --> 01:49:03,980
你什么都可以问我
You can ask me anything you want.

1864
01:49:04,320 --> 01:49:06,360
他在电视上干嘛？
ANDY: What the hell is he doing on television?

1865
01:49:06,700 --> 01:49:07,650
他整晚都在上面
He's on all night,

1866
01:49:07,750 --> 01:49:11,910
喊着要将他的案子告上最高法院
screaming about taking his lawsuit to the Supreme Court.

1867
01:49:12,580 --> 01:49:15,700
他真是疯了 他想将这带到华府去？
He really must be crazy. He's gonna go to Washington with this?

1868
01:49:16,630 --> 01:49:18,120
他简直是疯了
He's out of his fucking mind.

1869
01:49:18,210 --> 01:49:21,990
世上有这样的伪君子真是可叹 他们爱做什么就做什么
It's a pity we have such hypocrisy. Some people do what they want.

1870
01:49:22,130 --> 01:49:24,840
其他人却得承担后果 这就是人生
Other people have to pay through the nose. Such is life.

1871
01:49:25,260 --> 01:49:30,170
安迪，去找他 告诉他辞职的时候到了
Andy, go see him. Tell him maybe it's time he should quit.

1872
01:49:36,270 --> 01:49:39,020
第一点，他们的所做所为 完全的违反了宪法
SAM: First, what they did was totally unconstitutional.

1873
